Armed bandits are currently attacking villages in Shiroro Local Government Area, SaharaReporters can confirm. The bandits, who already wreaked havoc in Lakpma Village early on Monday morning, are currently operating in Kashua Village near Angwan Madi. SaharaReporters gathered that some villagers are currently on the run while others have been left at the mercy of the invaders. The response of the police to the developing situation is unclear at the time of filing this report.


Sahara Reporters Media